column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as SpecobjId   FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL  EXEC spExecuteSQL ' SELECT u.up_name as [name], s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, e.bpt, e.Flux_Hb_#,e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OI_#, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_SII_#, e.Flux_SII_# FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specObjID = x.specObjID WHERE  s.zWarning=# AND  s.class = GALAXY AND
